_sText: AWP_ITALY_ALLEY by 2ToW ** Just an simple awp map with box to take cover. Two "tunnels" in the side of the alley. Very fast gameplay! Good to train awp skill with bots. Bots are just so damn good with snipers. ** -32 Spawn points -Background music (doesn't work well!) -Fast gameplay -Simple layout ** Please, comment and asses!
